title: Quality Means Something Here. 2 Bedroom In Senior Community Available!
map_address: 8201 Sartain Drive near John T. White
posting_body: ['Make Cobblestone Manor your new home!', 'Our senior community offers one and two bedroom apartments that accommodate large living areas, a separate dining area, beautiful hardwood floors, and sparkling GE appliances in the kitchen including a full-size stove, microwave, refrigerator and dishwasher.', 'Plus, enjoy full-size washer and dryer connections designed to make every day functions as convenient as possible.', 'A spacious walk-in closet with built-in shelves completes this outstanding apartment.', 'Call today to make your new home at Cobblestone Manor!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Various Resident Activities', '- Granite Kitchen Countertops', '- Outside Storage Available', '- Utilities Included In Rent: Water', '- Sparkling Outdoor Pool', '- Clubhouse', '- Garbage Disposal', '- 24-Hour Community Fitness Center', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Cobblestone Manor is a 62+ senior apartment community that participates in a affordable housing, tax credit program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $38,820 | 2 Occupants: $44,340 | 3 Occupants: $49,860 | 4 Occupants: $55,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Cobblestone Manor', '8201 Sartain Drive', 'Fort Worth, TX, 76120', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'UK9hkZMuWrwV']
